<placeName>棣</placeName>
<measure quantity="2" unit="prefectures">
<num value="2">二</num>州</measure>
<pc>，</pc>遂以檢校工部<term>尚書</term>嗣領節度<pc>，</pc>而以<placeName>德州</placeName>
<term>刺史</term>
<persName>薛昌朝</persName>為保信軍<term>節度使</term>
<pc>，</pc>統德<pc>、</pc>棣<pc>。</pc>
